      "rendered_markdown": "# Community Energy Retrofit Impact Report\n\n**Audience:** public\n**Reporting period:** 2026 Q2\n\n## Executive summary\nCommunity Energy Retrofit Pilot reports governed impact evidence for 2026 Q2.\n\n## Initiative and goal\n**Community Energy Retrofit Pilot**\n\nReduce household energy burden while improving residential efficiency.\n\n## Results\n- Indicator: Average monthly bill reduction\n- Observed value: 18.0 USD\n- Period: 2026 Q2\n\n## Analysis\n- Saved analysis runs: 0\n- Scenarios: 0\n\n## Review and quality\n- Review workflow valid: True\n- Publications: 0\n\n## Methodology appendix\n- Canonical Contract Version: 1.1.0\n- Evidence Repository Version: 1.3.0\n- Indicator Registry Version: 1.4.0\n- Measurement Repository Version: 1.5.0\n- Review Workflow Version: 1.6.0\n- Analysis Repository Version: 1.7.0\n- Source Count: 1\n- Method Count: 1\n- Calculation Provenance: {}\n- Boundary: \n\n## Limitations\n- Validation tests consistency and traceability, not truth or source authenticity.\n- Observed change does not by itself establish attribution or causality.\n- Scenario and trend outputs are descriptive or planning artifacts, not verified forecasts.\n\n## References\n1. Unknown author (n.d.) Pilot utility-billing sample and participant survey summary. Internal pilot evidence package GIC-ENERGY-2026-Q2\n",
